## What Was Tried

| Approach | Result | Notes |
|----------|--------|-------|
| `first_dur < nominator` threshold | Too many false positives | 48%→39%, 34 improved, 28 regressed |
| `first_dur <= nominator/2` threshold | Better balance | 48%→~35%, 40 improved, 21 regressed |
| Last-measure confirmation (`last_dur > 0 && last_dur < nominator`) | Helps true pickups, no effect on FPs | Most pieces have last_dur=0 |
| Sub-voice splitting (upper/lower) | Fundamentally broken | SymbolChord mixes positions in same chord |
| Multi-voice consensus | Abandoned | Same SymbolChord mixing problem |
| Debug image analysis for FP pieces | Confirmed TrOmr model bias | Notes visible, barline misplaced |
| HOMR_PICKUP_DEBUG file-based logging | Works | Eval captures stderr, must use file path |

